  "question": "<p>(1) Can the EPA issue industry-wide regulations that categorically limit the amount of pollutants that existing manufacturing plants can discharge?</p>\n<p>(2) Does the Court of Appeals have jurisdiction to review the EPA regulations that apply to existing plants?</p>\n<p>(3) Can the EPA subject newly constructed manufacturing plants to exacting pollution standards that do not allow for any variance from the prescribed limit?</p>\n",
